page.title: 03Gary Campbell's Day.
page.content: Friday , I wake up at 7.00 am.At 7.30 I wash, then it is time for breakfast. For breakfast I have boiled egg. AT 8.30 I leave for school.We start school at 9.00 , then we have hymn practice at 9.45. When we come out of the hall we go back to class and we do handwriting.After that it is spelling workshop followed by maths. At 10.45 it is first play.After that we do English until 12.00 then it is dinner. I go home for dinner and cook myself a beef burger sandwich . At 12.45 I go back to school and do my African project until 2.30. For last break we play bulldog .After that we have P.E until the bell goes at 3.45 and I can go home for tea.
